<script>
export default {
  props: {
    group: {
      type: String,
      default: '',
    },
    position: {
      type: String,
      default: 'top',
      validator(value) {
        return ['top', 'bottom'].includes(value);
      },
    },
  },

  provide() {
    return {
      ['context']: { group: this.group, position: this.position },
    };
  },
  render() {
    return this.$slots.default({
      group: this.group,
    });
  },
};
</script>
